thread.title: Sue

author: Sue
title: Sue
text: I highly recommend the service provided by Nelson Alexander. The information about the campaign and sale process was detailed and comprehensive and the support Grant provided throughout, including at times when I needed advice and support regarding decisions, was extremely helpful. Selling one's home is not an easy process but Nelson Alexander's approach and attention to detail inspired confidence throughout.
